                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l29">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> dıe <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l30"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin beſant vnd
                                <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit Jr geredt daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l31">ſie ſolch <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd klag
                        yecʒo gegen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>langh<ex>ans</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l32">auf <expan>geiſtlıche<ex>m</ex></expan> gerihte
                        vallen laſſen vnd das reht vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l33">euch darümb nemen vvil .
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . vvenn dıeſelb
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_571_r1l34">Burgerin <del rend="strikethrough">darümb </del> oder
